snippet.title: Mahou Sensei Negima! – Private Lesson 2 – Ojamashimasuu Parasite de Chuu Japan - HashROM.com
snippet.description:
Mahou Sensei Negima! Private Lessions 2, or known better in the Japanese version Mahou Sensei Negima! Private Lessions 2: Bothering You to Parasite by Ju~ (魔法先生ネギま! プライベートレッスン2 お邪魔しますぅ パラサイトでチュ〜, Mahō Sensei Negima! Puraibēto Ressun 2 Ojamashimasu~u Parasaito de Chu〜) is the sequel to Mahou Sensei Negima! Private Lessons for the Game Boy Advance.

Download GBA/CIA at: https://hashrom.com/mahou-sensei-negima-private-lesson-2-ojamashimasuu-parasite-de-chuu-japan/
